title: Arctic_Monkeys-Favourite_Worst_Nightmare-2007-MST
description:
Album Description
Favourite Worst Nightmare is everything you
hoped Arctic Monkeys would do next. Not so
much a sequel as an upgrade, a breakneck
technicolour journey through screwball punk
and guitar-fuelled dancefloor heroics, it\&#039;s
very, very fast and very, very loud; a
brilliant racket that proves there\&#039;s
infinitely more to Arctic Monkeys than
writing pretty little ditties, yet at the
same time boasting some of the strongest
songs they\&#039;ve ever written.
